snippet.title: Freja And The False Prophecy - Cinematic Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Find us on Kickstarter to see more: https://kck.st/2Q5FbpY
A tale written in blood. A mystery to uncover. A journey of self discovery. Freja and the False Prophecy is a dark 2d action-adventure game set in the world of norse mythology.
